workouts.title: Weight Training Workout
workouts.description: Wide range of weight training exercises

exercises.title: Goblin squat
exercises.description: Works out the butt, thighs and hamstrings
exercises.tips:
1. Feet shoulder width apart. 
2. Keep heels on ground.

exercises.title: Dumbbell bench press
exercises.description: Focuses on chest, biceps and core
exercises.tips:
1. Exhale when pushing the bar upwards. 
2. Flex your abdomen when you're struggling to finish the last rep.

exercises.title: Reverse peck files
exercises.description: Trains the back, biceps, triceps and shoulders
exercises.tips:
1. Keep knees slightly bent. 
2. Keep arms at 90 degree angles.

exercises.title: Bicep curls
exercises.tips:
1. Palms face toward your thighs when arm is extended. 
2. Palms face your chest when bicep is flexed.

exercises.title: In-line lunges with weight
exercises.description: Works out the thighs, hamstrings and core

exercises.title: Power squat
exercises.tips:
1. Land quietly on toes. 
2. Legs stay at least shoulder width apart.

exercises.title: Inchworm plank suicides
exercises.tips:
1. Keep you back in neutral position when in a plank position. 
2. Alternate which arm you push the ground first to get up.

exercises.title: Plank jacks
exercises.tips:
1. Keep a neutral back. 
2. Doing it on your forearms is harder than doing the movement on your hands.

exercises.title: Jack knives
exercises.tips:
1. Keep feet, legs, arms and hands off the ground the whole time. 
2. Try to touch your toes when coming up.

workouts.title: Upper Body and Core
workouts.description: A set exercises focusing on strengthing abs and upper body

exercises.title: Scissors
exercises.description: Impacts core, back, butt and hip flexors
exercises.tips:
1. Keep your hands at your sides the entire time. 
2. Kick your feet as fast as you can.

exercises.title: Spider planks
exercises.tips: 1. Get your knees as close to your elbows as possible.

exercises.title: Push up
exercises.tips:
1. Go down untill your arms reach 90 degress. 
2. Keep your back neutral.

exercises.title: Shoulder pushup
exercises.description: Focuses on biceps, shoulders and streches out calves
exercises.tips:
1. Keep your legs straight. 
2. Make sure your hands are wider than shoulder witdth apart.

workouts.title: Lower Body
workouts.description: A set exercises focusing on strengthing lower body

exercises.title: Air squats
exercises.tips:
1. Landquietly on your toes. 
2. Keep feet at least shoulder width apart.

exercises.title: Toe taps
exercises.tips:
1. Keep your body on top of the ball. 
2. Light jumps, keeping on your toes.

exercises.title: Blateral step-out squat
exercises.description: Trains butt, thighs, hamstrings and calves
exercises.tips: 1. Lift the leg your're landing on next, up first and then leap to the side.

exercises.title: Lying leg lift
exercises.description: Exercises core, butt, back and hip flexors
